name: Interactive CD Sampler Pack Volume One
overview: Interactive CD Sampler Disc Volume 1 is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Various and published by SCEA, which was released in 1995. It includes playable demos of the following retail games: Loaded, Mortal Kombat 3, Twisted Metal, Warhawk, and Wipeout. Includes movies of the following games: Descent, Destruction Derby, NFL Game Day, and NHL Face Off. Includes the following hidden demo (unlocked via patch): Doom
